rComments: Loved the teacher helped a bunch.

People complain he is monotone and boring, but if you actually listen he is very articulate, clear, and relates everything to real life examples. He never bored me. Lecturesnotes are mainly pictures with minimal text, so you MUST attend lecture to get information! Midterm and noncumulative final, plus a paper and easy discussion section grade.

Professor Schneider is very nice and patient.He has got not only attractive voice but neat logic to clearly explain things. He uses many vivid examples and graphs to help you understand, though these will also appear in the exams.

Dr. Schneider is a great professor who is extremely knowledgeable. His style of using real-world case studies makes class engaging. However it is important to note that to succeed in this class you have to go to every single lecture. This class truly showed me why it is important to recognize natural systems within urban areas.
